'''钩蛾亚科'''（学名：Drepaninae）是[[鱗翅目|鱗翅目]][[钩蛾科|钩蛾科]]的一[[亚科|亚科]]，本亚科所属钩蛾一般身体狭长，无密毛，一般都有[[喙|喙]]，翅缰发达，[[蛹|蛹]]没有次生[[刚毛|刚毛]]{{r|zgdwz}}。
'''Drepaninae''' are by far the largest [[subfamily|subfamily]] of the [[Drepanidae|Drepanidae]] [[moth|moth]]s. While it is usually split into two [[tribe_(biology)|tribes]], '''Drepanini''' and '''Oretini''', its internal [[systematics|systematics]] and [[phylogeny|phylogeny]] are not well resolved.

